id":"292e0f9e7ab39efdcf291953a4f95bdf94e145e6","tid":1820561,"uid":193969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T14:46:08.000Z","msg":"有冇啲治安/生活/風土文化嘅嘢要小心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T19:33:54.000Z","msg":"去加德滿都嘅話睇下你接唔接受到空氣差"},{"pid":"5886499e5de86fc769a8813bb82ce0080ed41f80","tid":1820561,"uid":221247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T07:48:04.000Z","msg":"唔洗打疫苗<br />\n帶定口罩 加都幾大塵<br />\n小心揀餐廳/街邊野食 帶定啲肚痾藥<br />\n無其他野要小心<br />\n利申：去過尼泊爾兩星期"},{"pid":"db93943c4af743df51fbd6eb8832407952e004cf","tid":1820561,"uid":311570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:11:08.000Z","msg":"去過，冇打過疫苗。<br />\n好多佛教建築，要注意返人哋啲傳統。<br />\n<br />\n飲食方面，平日買樽裝水。自問腸胃算好差，餐廳揀啲普普通通嘅，好彩都冇肚屙。Momo同咖喱味道都好好食，啤酒可以選Nepal Ice。<br />\n<br />\n如果冇諗住上山，建議必到景點Pokhara和Nagarkot，風景都一流。加都就主要睇建築物。<br />\n<br />\nNagarkot住宿可以考慮呢間：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hotelcountryvilla/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhotelcountryvilla%2F&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWWo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=62ee6bb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hotelcountryvilla/</a><br />\n請自行睇相。"},{"pid":"8a20964caf3ca84085b46e42e85816826385f577","tid":1820561,"uid":19891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T12:02:08.000Z","msg":"如果唔行ebc/ abc等係米冇野好做?"},{"pid":"f21d77e0fd4f600a5425e8872b66021034c26460","tid":1820561,"uid":265932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a20964caf3ca84085b46e42e85816826385f577","tid":1820561,"uid":19891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T12:02:08.000Z","msg":"如果唔行ebc/ abc等係米冇野好做?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T13:01:46.000Z","msg":"仲有好多戶外活動"},{"pid":"76677caa294de9929142f73cdd0f12d269d615b0","tid":1820561,"uid":19891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f21d77e0fd4f600a5425e8872b6602103